{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"04c1d5a86b","title":"中央首长第三次接见河南赴京汇报代表团纪要","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a5166a9b6d","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":14,"articleId":"04c1d5a86b","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"戚本禹","id":"57434e107b","type":"人物"},{"name":"康生","id":"57eea82497","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"周总理","id":"838b5f2c9d","type":"人物"},{"name":"文敏生","id":"9047f04de9","type":"人物"},{"name":"谢富治","id":"93cca4665d","type":"人物"},{"name":"纪登奎","id":"9a50528209","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"贺龙","id":"d0a2337495","type":"人物"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"杨成武","id":"e1397e909a","type":"人物"},{"name":"陈伯达","id":"e46e45351b","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"48606ca4e5","name":"陈伯达"},{"id":"8bb7755376","name":"康生"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b0a217b016","type":"title","text":"中央首长第三次接见河南赴京汇报代表团纪要","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"447c60a47b","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：1967年6月14日晚9点40分至凌晨2点40分，地点：人民大会堂安徽厅。中央首长：周总理、陈伯达、康生、谢富治、杨成武、戚本禹。出席代表：二七公社、开封八·二四、河造总、以及新乡、洛阳、焦作、鹤壁双方代表。省委干部：纪登奎、耿其昌、王庭栋、纪的秘书、文敏生、赵文甫、杨蔚屏、戴苏理。军区：何运洪、张树芝、余嗣贵、李善亭。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"363d637d1c","type":"paragraph","text":"开始“二七公社”高呼口号（略），对方也呼。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e3893bbb5d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们的口号喊清楚点，不要把自己的口号也加在里边，不然我们不举手。这是我们戚本禹这个青年人提的。……（大笑）","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bb42c5d2a6","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：我讲一点，在中央开会时，用不着读语录，用不着呼口号。我再说一遍（又重复一遍），另外，不管你们那一边，千万要遵守纪律，要摆事实，讲道理，要讲慢点，讲清楚。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cf862f6c24","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们年纪和我差一大截，你们说那么快，我怎么跟得上。（哄然大笑）我们把各地都请来了，有开封的、有新乡的、有焦作的、鹤壁的，信阳的、洛阳的、偃师的，兰考的也来了。郑州的听得多了，这次听听外地的。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a4fe0d30aa","type":"paragraph","text":"郑大战斗师：我们郑大战斗师还没发言。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a1f0b7f409","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：等一下（造总代表不由分说起来发言）","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"29dd27db4a","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（发火）等一下嘛，我再三地讲你们要守纪律，听总理讲嘛！","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9570759cbd","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：开封八·二四讲。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"865a5eff08","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：我，李福来。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e19140a52e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：查名单（戚本禹插话说是李福来）","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1fef1cf1b3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：好！李福来讲，不要太长，最多20多分钟。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"19e1371720","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：何运洪和赵静生都是一个腔调，要不把八月的造反派打成御用工具就糟了（对方跳起来说造谣）","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"beac029abf","type":"paragraph","text":"（总理、康老阻止对方发言。）","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d002f524ea","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们这成习惯了，一触即发这是要犯错误的，我给你们介绍经验，一触即跳必定要犯错误。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc86cbf06a","type":"paragraph","text":"（李福来继续讲）","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fa5d246254","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：什么时候定你们反动组织？谁定的？","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8480912889","type":"paragraph","text":"（李回答了时间，李谈到军队宣传车喊“贺龙万岁”。）","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ecd94d588","type":"paragraph","text":"戚本禹：谁喊的？","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"728134de2c","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：8172的宣传车。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"97cc250d4e","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：有这事吗？","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7474eb8c12","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：不仅一次，16、17、18连续多次（李举出时间地点并举出一车号是午4－16－94）","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c81d314a12","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们把主席象砸烂了吗？","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b8a787c0d9","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：纯粹造谣。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"57ef0a0ec2","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：你们搞了个四条吗？","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0c7bbbe6ff","type":"paragraph","text":"（李作了详细的说明，并拿出笔记本上的原始材料说明是断章取义，政治陷害。）","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1cfc904141","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：（满意地点了头，并接过笔记本仔细阅后面带微笑地转交给陈伯达同志。）","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"905a762ffb","type":"paragraph","text":"（李谈二·八事件、二·一一事件、二·一八流血事件打死二人时，戚和总理在一块研究记录）","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f56fad5ebb","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：打死的叫什么名字？","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"055969334d","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四（黄泽生）：杜聚明，化建公司木工，35岁。","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"751c1a012d","type":"paragraph","text":"康生：哪里人？","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f2d363f1ce","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：开封市人。","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"691629941a","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：女的？","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b83e9e58a0","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：孙爱英、开封青年农场女工，被赤卫队掐死的。","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b31edbe9b","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：那女的当时送家里了？","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"87043c16ec","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：是不是送家里的不清楚。","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d1160d7a38","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：等了几天？","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"122c83bc32","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：八天。","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b0262bbf6d","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：怎么死的？","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"df654bbe4d","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四（黄泽生）：掐死的。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6c96d8e76a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理、戚本禹：谁运走的？","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"426f55f6b5","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四（黄）：八·二四同学。","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"359ca08a9f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：谁开的枪？","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0798f17b44","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四（李）：一驻军战士。","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bedcc1766b","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：弹头？","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6ddaf895bb","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四（李）：出来了。","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7d942aef8","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：没找到？","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2b2c20dd7d","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：没有。当时队伍打乱了，有医生诊断，有伤口分寸。","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"59157534c0","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：材料带来了？","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b41f7b6ef4","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：带来了，下边可交首长。","index":50,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8e406a2744","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（仔细听李讲。）","index":51,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4792f0b8bf","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：八·二四被捕615人，占八·二四的34％。","index":52,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2fc85b67fa","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：打死在二月十九号？","index":53,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"62b822b976","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：二月十八日晚上。","index":54,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c01231375c","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：八·二四多少人？","index":55,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"126bfb0cb6","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：1600多人。被捕600多人。","index":56,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4681d489dc","type":"paragraph","text":"（作记录）","index":57,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cb99930ce7","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：被捕600多人。","index":58,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d711b06577","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：劳动改造多少？","index":59,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"adf36901ea","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：57人。","index":60,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"12a4df2c31","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：放了没有？","index":61,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"687172d468","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：放了。","index":62,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"54dfdcf5ab","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：宣传车是你们砸的吗？有这事吗？","index":63,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11ddb50840","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：没有。","index":64,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"22b1ac9e28","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：抢了枪了吗？","index":65,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bf3dfce2d7","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：没有。","index":66,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"308a5f30f5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：六号门有枪吗？","index":67,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a42bbdfe1a","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四（黄泽生）：公安公社逮捕六号门负责人秦俭时，群众气愤地把公安公社枪下了，当时交给电厂武装部。","index":68,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b9f2256611","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四（李）：从2月8日至3月中旬开封捕4千人。2月18日抓一千多人。","index":69,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3724951d65","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：师院抓2000人？","index":70,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"46e2360f1e","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：600多人。","index":71,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"90277ab26a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你讲快点，你讲的差不多了。你别把今晚的时间都讲了，要集中点，有材料把材料交上来。我们记者站的同志明天还以座谈的形式找各地谈，把材料交上来，不然每个地方都要听，时间不允许。四川就是这样。","index":72,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7ec47d6e20","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：好，快点。摧垮的保守组织复活，以开封师院为例。","index":73,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09a6ebc83c","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：他们现在成造反派了（李讲到井冈山时），噢，你对井冈山有什么看法？","index":74,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"388fa1b41a","type":"paragraph","text":"八·二四：地地道道的保皇派。（这时开封师院井冈山跳起来大叫：造谣。）","index":75,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"14ece95ba5","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你是开封师院的？（井冈山：是）","index":76,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd5a59e604","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：井冈山的？（井冈山：是）","index":77,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"404711d9f7","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：哈哈，对头啊！（井冈山起来发言）","index":78,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"26a8b1d81b","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你讲快些，人家还要讲嘛！（……）","index":79,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"615a1d13dc","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：兰考有人来吗？（有，总理，我要求发言）。","index":80,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7fe739baa9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你等一等，还让他讲。（井冈山又讲，当他否认自己是保皇派时）","index":81,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1fb8330f9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们杀出来是今年了吧？（井冈山：不是！）（八·二四欲反驳）","index":82,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"136f03b9f3","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（对八·二四）你不要接人家的话，你把东西拿出来嘛！","index":83,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fb227dcfe3","type":"paragraph","text":"（八·二四交给总理一份井冈山成立声明）","index":84,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef9c581844","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（对井冈山）你们今年二月二十四日的声明，（把声明举起来一股劲地摇）承认井冈山兵团前段执行了资产阶级反动路线。","index":85,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b5dcfe7b9e","type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山：当时他们压我们很厉害，把我们压垮了。","index":86,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e4d3da1b08","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：压是一回事，你们执行资产阶级反动路线又是一回事，你讲一下。","index":87,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"50526dc1ba","type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山：那……那时……（吞吞吐吐地）","index":88,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e595e2aef2","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们自己的事嘛。","index":89,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ee8d068bfc","type":"paragraph","text":"井冈山：那是几个人起草的，没通过……","index":90,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e58dc4be97","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：起草没关系，怎么能油印呢？这下边落款还是你们兵团的名字嘛！","index":91,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"647b535e4d","type":"paragraph","text":"（井冈山吞吞吐吐，狼狈不堪，又讲八·二四的“罪状”，拿出许多照片……）","index":92,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96f058d4c7","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你要扼要点，这里材料比你还多。（井冈山又讲了一会）","index":93,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f889975625","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你等一下，我问一件事，北航×××来了吗？","index":94,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8b8483bc8f","type":"paragraph","text":"红代会：没有。","index":95,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f107559e48","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们来几个？","index":96,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bcf3f56944","type":"paragraph","text":"红代会：六个。","index":97,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c288f0cb0f","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：都是哪个学校的？","index":98,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c54780e568","type":"paragraph","text":"红代会：地质二人，农机二人，石油一人，北大一人。","index":99,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a9e09945ba","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：通知另一方面，清华、北航、北工有人支持造总的，也让他们进来。（红代会答：支持是少数。）不管多数少数，有支持的让他们进来。","index":100,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9b9355454b","type":"paragraph","text":"红代会：是这样的，他们每个总部，比如北航红旗、清华井冈山总部都是支持二七的。","index":101,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e6f7951a0f","type":"paragraph","text":"支持造总的只是个别人，不能代表总部的观点，没有经过红代会的批准。","index":102,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"550c749ff1","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：你们是红代会批准的。","index":103,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33641b59cb","type":"paragraph","text":"红代会：我们是红代会特派河南战斗队，是红代会批准的。","index":104,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a4bceb186e","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：噢，你们是正式批准的，（造总递了条子要求让他们进来）这个事交给谢副总理。（总理将条子递给谢副总理，谢看后没吭声。）","index":105,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea6e68d8e3","type":"paragraph","text":"（井冈山又讲，总理和康老等首长在看材料）","index":106,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"95bb12cc19","type":"paragraph","text":"（井冈山讲到纪登奎、开封第一书记徐学龙收买八·二四，给了70万元）","index":107,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"471a556569","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：（不满地问）谁给的钱？什么钱？有什么证据？你要快一点，离题太远了！（走出去了。）","index":108,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"87a9733245","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：听我讲，我们现在要听一下洛阳的情况，因为现在洛阳情况很严重。请洛阳拖拉机学校的常春波同志讲。","index":109,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bf2864016a","type":"paragraph","text":"（洛阳的常春波讲了，讲得很慢、很生，没有感情，主要讲洛阳的武斗的情况）（二七群众很生气；老保得逞，跳起来说什么不会造谣，我们讲。）","index":110,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3e5eed6bec","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（仍然非常耐心地听他讲，仔细地询问）你讲的是军区还是军分区？","index":111,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f96735681","type":"paragraph","text":"常：是何运洪搞的……（对方嘲笑）","index":112,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"053d434ce9","type":"paragraph","text":"（康老点了点头）（当常谈到洛阳武斗影响了生产）","index":113,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7c49490270","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（惊讶地问）拖拉机厂停工了？！","index":114,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5a876820c8","type":"paragraph","text":"（老保门不承认是他们挑起武斗，乱吵吵）你们八一六是什么组织？包括不包括工人？工厂是什么组织？（常作了回答。）","index":115,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bd3039d348","type":"paragraph","text":"红代会：（尤红）：拖拉机厂筹委会去围攻的。","index":116,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b403b8082e","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：现在还围着吗。（常答：攻破了！）","index":117,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67eac823bf","type":"paragraph","text":"（公安厅红色公安几次要求发言，想在首长面前无情地揭露公安公社黑幕）","index":118,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6cb76f5f89","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：等一下，围攻哪里？（常答：机务段。）我没听清，噢，机务段……","index":119,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69e3988698","type":"paragraph","text":"公安厅的张××：发生在六六通令后。","index":120,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f098a90865","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（点头）张捷是什么人：（常答：洛阳市武装部长，参加围攻）","index":121,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dbfd3a5258","type":"paragraph","text":"（老保：造谣！）","index":122,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1872efb97b","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（对老保）我说了，你认为他是造谣，那不是对你有利吗？逮捕了二百多人放了没有？有没有再捕人？","index":123,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7b5728726","type":"paragraph","text":"张××：洛阳捕人了（老保：造谣。）","index":124,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"af97b2fd2e","type":"paragraph","text":"（张××同志要求揭发公安厅内幕，老保急得跳了起来，攻击张××是投机倒把分子。这时红代会同志要求发言，场面较乱。）","index":125,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"28c92ec916","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：慢慢地让他（指常）讲吗。你是红代会的，等一等，你有材料送上来好了。","index":126,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da7ad1c4ad","type":"paragraph","text":"常：有1000多人跑出来到八机部住着，还有的跑到其他地方。","index":127,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"92dcfe6ff5","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：有没有捕人？（常：没有。）","index":128,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a4125def0","type":"paragraph","text":"常：八一六大楼被围，上面有300多人。","index":129,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5be8dc9b54","type":"paragraph","text":"尤红：我要发言。（老保跳起来指着尤红：你尤红是专门挑起挑斗的！）","index":130,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6a03806d55","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你哪一位？（老保：我洛阳的。）洛阳的正在讲吗！（老保：我们有材料补充。）你有材料交上来好了！（常继续讲）","index":131,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a5114a908","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：火车停了？","index":132,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5bb5fa403b","type":"paragraph","text":"常：6月9日全部停运，工人不敢上班，被毒打被抓走！","index":133,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e7a2ef294b","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：扼要点！（常：在洛阳出现了一股炮打无产阶级司令部的妖风，写出了许多反动标语。）（老保：我们没有，是你搞的，欺骗中央。）","index":134,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b585cb98a1","type":"paragraph","text":"尤红：有！是你们干的！（老保反驳，要压制尤红发言，攻击首都红代会战友挑起武斗。）","index":135,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e8d60a5e43","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：他们（尤红等）是中央请来的，发言不发言中央有权力，不能由你们决定（对老保）（后又对尤红）你是红代会农机学院的吗？人家点了名啦！你有权利反驳，你把材料整一下交上来，交给戚本禹同志，这关系到你们红代会的声誉。（说着和戚本禹、周总理同时大笑……）","index":136,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bccc2dbd73","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：（对老保）你讲！不要激动，造反有理，一激动就没有理啦！","index":137,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"db51f06e14","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：那是观点不同？（老保讲……）","index":138,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"915e2551e2","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：我想现在请洛阳的同志说明一点，现在还有没有武斗？有武斗如何制止？这是我们当前的迫切任务。洛阳是重工业城市，（在洛阳武斗）对国家不利。（老保还要继续讲）","index":139,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7847db9844","type":"paragraph","text":"谢：停下来！","index":140,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"43b983876f","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：停下来！","index":141,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"96b442f055","type":"paragraph","text":"（常又讲。老保：造谣！）","index":142,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b799fe082","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你们让人家讲嘛，何必左一个造谣右一个造谣。","index":143,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"10e9048875","type":"paragraph","text":"刘生：制止武斗我有办法，只要解放军站在公正的立场就能制止。","index":144,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"25553282d6","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：对！军队应该徒手解围制止武斗。双方都要制止武斗。破坏了国家财产，损坏了身体，不好！（老保又讲）我谈一句，有个叫刘峰的是哪一位？（河造总的捣乱分子站了起来（康老发火了）你递了两个条子，说有要事告诉我们，你有什么事怎么不写出来呢？这事并没有什么好保密的！请新乡的讲吧！新乡已发出呼吁了，你（老保）到过新乡吗？（没有，）你没有到过新乡，你讲啥！你的意思我明白了！你有材料你写出来吧。","index":145,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"43a85cff2a","type":"paragraph","text":"（新乡八一八李德森讲，最近八一八被围困、断粮断炊的情况，康老很关切地询问了情况。接着新乡李玉坤讲，当讲到他是参加了老红卫兵时）","index":146,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a36a800ad2","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你是老红卫兵，什么时候成立的？（李回答）噢，你老红卫兵是八月二十四日成立的，八一八红卫兵是9月1日成立的，相差一个星期就老了。在北京老红卫兵人家就从另外地方想……（说着笑了）","index":147,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"29dacd5469","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：（对李玉坤）时间很宝贵。","index":148,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4308b927e9","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：新乡最近逮人没有？刚才那个同学讲八号捕人了……粮食站封锁了没有？老保李玉坤讲他们也被断粮的情况欺骗中央首长，李玉坤油头滑面地讲个不停）。","index":149,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"67cfbfbc67","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：你把材料交过来！","index":150,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e0a7681954","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达：你说的多了把主要问题都冲淡了。（新乡师院八一八要求辟谣。）","index":151,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea4112476c","type":"paragraph","text":"康、陈：你们可以辟谣。（新乡八一八发言，李玉坤立即起来吵吵。）","index":152,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0bd96ad0b9","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：焦作的谈吧！（焦作矿院八一八刘文学讲，焦作老保不讲道理的抢着发言，刘文学一看是个四不清干部，气愤地说：你没有资格发言）","index":153,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f8addaa7f6","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：这儿谁都可以谈。（老保讲了下去，当他骂耿其昌老混蛋时）","index":154,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"046b4fec09","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：在这儿不要骂人，摆事实讲道理，在中央开会不要骂人！（面带怒色）你是不是抢了章子（指假夺权）的？你要讲扼要点，你从开始讲，讲一天也讲不完！焦作矿院八一八讲，讲了大方向，很有声色，时间到了……","index":155,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"681ac9deda","type":"paragraph","text":"戚：今天就停下来。","index":156,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a8d314c576","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：今天谈到这儿，以后谈，以后来谈。郑大战斗师不属于两派，可以写材料。下一次十大总部各总部来两个人。","index":157,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1300932122","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：尤红把材料送上来。","index":158,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"123f198fba","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：洛阳打群架很厉害，不符合六条通令。要百分之百地执行六六通令，军分区无论如何要劝阻，派不带武装的。军区除一军负责的地方要多负责任，把武斗劝阻。生产下降的尤其是洛阳，还有煤矿，平顶山，焦作，还有铁路全部军管。有权制止武斗，我刚才……去广西那边，一国际列车94个小时停在柳州，复杂了。把农民调到车站打司机，司机受伤，把车开到柳州停下来。要交打人凶手，不交出打人凶手不开车，这多不好！运往越南前线的，国际影响也不好。徐州也搞得不好。郑州是关键地方，不管怎样打架，不要打到铁路上来，一切为运输服务……你们双方打电话，不要讲下去，算了。","index":159,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"75018a4592","type":"paragraph","text":"康老：总是讲过去，这怎么行呢？","index":160,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"faecf3f77c","type":"paragraph","text":"总理：军管会，大军区管，武汉军区管，不得支持一方打击一方。军管会是站在中央的立场上……散会。（双方吵，总理很生气。）（大家呼口号！）","index":161,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"abc9da0768","type":"paragraph","text":"（二七战士高呼，毛主席万岁！第三次汇报结束。）","index":162,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"04c1d5a86b","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}